                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-955-18540814 t18540814-955-punishment-82"></join>Confined Nine Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Baron Martin.</hi>
